{"lemma":"غُرْفَةٌ","slug":"غُرْفَةٌ","root":"غ.ر.ف","root_slug":"غ-ر-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غُرْفَة","root":"غرف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31700"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"room, compartment, cell, chamber","examples":[{"text":"غُرْفَةُ الْمَعِيشَةِ","english":"The living room"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the quantity of water laded out with the hand","examples":[{"text":"فَلَمَّا فَصَلَ طَالُوتُ بِالْجُنُودِ قَالَ إِنَّ اللَّهَ مُبْتَلِيكُم بِنَهَرٍ فَمَن شَرِبَ مِنْهُ فَلَيْسَ مِنِّي وَمَن لَّمْ يَطْعَمْهُ فَإِنَّهُ مِنِّي إِلَّا مَنِ اغْتَرَفَ غُرْفَةً بِيَدِهِ ۚ فَشَرِبُوا مِنْهُ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا مِّنْهُمْ ۚ فَلَمَّا جَاوَزَهُ هُوَ وَالَّذِينَ آمَنُوا مَعَهُ قَالُوا لَا طَاقَةَ لَنَا الْيَوْمَ بِجَالُوتَ وَجُنُودِهِ ۚ قَالَ الَّذِينَ يَظُنُّونَ أَنَّهُم مُّلَاقُو اللَّهِ كَم مِّن فِئَةٍ قَلِيلَةٍ غَلَبَتْ فِئَةً كَثِيرَةً بِإِذْنِ اللَّهِ ۗ وَاللَّهُ مَعَ الصَّابِرِينَ","english":"When Saul marched forth with his army, he cautioned: “Allah will test you with a river. So whoever drinks ˹his fill˺ from it is not with me, and whoever does not taste it—except a sip from the hollow of his hands—is definitely with me.” They all drank ˹their fill˺ except for a few! When he and the ˹remaining˺ faithful with him crossed the river, they said, “Now we are no match for Goliath and his warriors.” But those ˹believers˺ who were certain they would meet Allah reasoned, “How many times has a small force vanquished a mighty army by the Will of Allah! And Allah is ˹always˺ with the steadfast.”"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of غَرَفَ (ḡarafa)","examples":[{"text":"اِمْتَلَأَ الوِعَاءُ مِنْ أَوَّلِ غَرْفَةٍ","english":"The pot was filled from the first scoop."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the quantity of water laded out with the hand"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mode of lading with the hand"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sandal"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣur.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31700","headword_ar":"غُرْفَةٌ","root":"grf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is taken"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laded out"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as with a ladle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (JK, S, * Mgh, * O, Msb, * K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as much"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as fills the hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guraAfapN","text_ar":"غُرَافَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (O, K:) before it is so taken it is not termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurofap","text_ar":"غُرْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAfN","text_ar":"غِرَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Somewhat remaining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of milk. (IAar, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzE","text_ar":"جزع"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euil~iy~apN","text_ar":"عُِلِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, Msb, K;) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An upper chamber;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a chamber in the upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, story:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 325:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurafN","text_ar":"غُرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurafaAtN","text_ar":"غُرَفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) which latter is held by some to be a pl. pl. (Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurufaAtN","text_ar":"غُرُفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurofaAtN","text_ar":"غُرْفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algurofapu","text_ar":"الغُرْفَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Seventh Heaven:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, * K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the highest of the places of Paradise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or it is one of the names of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paradise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xxv. 75.) Accord. to the S [and O], the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna gurofapi","text_ar":"دُونَ غُرْفَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earo$ihi","text_ar":"عَرْشِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a verse of Lebeed, as applying to the Seventh Heaven: but what is [found] in his poetry is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna Eiz~api Earo$ihi","text_ar":"دُونَ عِزَّةِ عَرْشِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IB, TA.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lock"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSolap","text_ar":"خُصْلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of hair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cord, tied with a bow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"double bow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoquwdN","text_ar":"مَعْقُودٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^uno$uwTapK","text_ar":"بِاُنْشُوطَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is put upon the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hung upon the neck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) of the dial. of El-Yemen. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","S","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}